 in this study is provided as a public Python package\npyGenISW. This could be used in the future studies for constructing the ISW\nfrom existing and future simulation suites probing vast sets of cosmological\nparameters and models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Mar 2021 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 12:02:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
