 1-norm in quantum computing for quantum chemistry,\nand provides simple ways of decreasing its value to reduce the complexity of\nquantum algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Mar 2021 22:05:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 07:32:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Oct 2021 10:33:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
